## Compare the four

### Slice

* ordered
* flexible size
* most common sequence type in Go

### Array

* ordered
* fixed size
* less common in everyday application code

### Map

* key-value storage
* fast lookup by key

### Struct

* named fields
* best for one clearly structured record

