## Indexing reminder

Go slices and arrays use **zero-based indexing**.

```go
package main

import "fmt"

func main() {
    colors := []string{"red", "blue", "green"}
    fmt.Println(colors[0])
    fmt.Println(colors[1])
    fmt.Println(colors[2])
}
```

