### A. Append to a slice

```go
tasks := []string{"email", "backup"}
tasks = append(tasks, "deploy")
fmt.Println(tasks)
```

### B. Use a typed map

```go
scores := map[string]int{
    "math": 95,
    "science": 88,
}
fmt.Println(scores["math"])
```

### C. Struct literal

```go
